00:46:54,040 --> 00:46:55,600
said Dudley suddenly.

1256
00:46:55,600 --> 00:46:56,840
"Dad, Harry's got something!"

1257
00:46:57,440 --> 00:46:59,800
Harry was on the point of unfolding his letter,

1258
00:46:59,800 --> 00:47:02,760
