1475
00:55:14,840 --> 00:55:17,760
but Harry leapt into the air trying to catch one.

1476
00:55:17,760 --> 00:55:19,280
"Out! OUT!"

1477
00:55:19,280 --> 00:55:22,920
Uncle Vernon seized Harry around the 
waist and threw him into the hall.

1478
00:55:22,920 --> 00:55:26,680
When Aunt Petunia and Dudley had run 
out with their arms over their faces,

1479
00:55:26,680 --> 00:55:28,800
Uncle Vernon slammed the door shut.

1480
00:55:28,800 --> 00:55:31,360
They could hear the letters 
still streaming into the room,

1481
00:55:31,360 --> 00:55:33,480
bouncing off the walls and floor.

1482
00:55:33,480 --> 00:55:34,080
"That does it,"

1483
00:55:34,080 --> 00:55:35,200
said Uncle Vernon,

1484
00:55:35,200 --> 00:55:39,920
trying to speak calmly but pulling great 
tufts out of his mustache at the same time.

1485
00:55:39,920 --> 00:55:42,800
I want you all back here in 
five minutes ready to leave.

1486
00:55:42,800 --> 00:55:44,040
We're going away.

1487
00:55:44,040 --> 00:55:45,640
Just pack some clothes.

1488
00:55:45,640 --> 00:55:46,920
No arguments!"

1489
00:55:46,920 --> 00:55:51,200
He looked so dangerous with half his 
mustache missing that no one dared argue.

1490
00:55:51,200 --> 00:55:54,160
Ten minutes later they had wrenched 
their way through the boarded-up doors

1491
00:55:54,160 --> 00:55:55,280
and were in the car,

1492
00:55:55,280 --> 00:55:56,960
speeding toward the highway.

1493
00:55:56,960 --> 00:55:59,040
Dudley was sniffling in the back seat;

1494
