really looking forward to.

2983
01:49:34,520 --> 01:49:36,960
The last shop was narrow and shabby.

2984
01:49:36,960 --> 01:49:43,040
Peeling gold letters over the door read 
Ollivanders: Makers of Fine Wands since 382 B.C.

2985
01:49:43,040 --> 01:49:47,360
A single wand lay on a faded 
purple cushion in the dusty window.

2986
01:49:47,360 --> 01:49:51,840
A tinkling bell rang somewhere in the 
depths of the shop as they stepped inside.

2987
01:49:51,840 --> 01:49:53,080
It was a tiny place,

2988
01:49:53,080 --> 01:49:54,640
empty except for a single,

2989
