3088
01:53:19,800 --> 01:53:20,440
"Right then,

3089
01:53:20,440 --> 01:53:21,600
Mr. Potter.

3090
01:53:21,600 --> 01:53:22,640
Try this one.

3091
01:53:22,640 --> 01:53:24,640
Beechwood and dragon heartstring.

3092
01:53:24,640 --> 01:53:25,880
Nine inches.

3093
01:53:25,880 --> 01:53:27,280
Nice and flexible.

3094
01:53:27,280 --> 01:53:29,200
