3101
01:53:47,800 --> 01:53:49,520
"No, no -here,

3102
01:53:49,520 --> 01:53:51,360
ebony and unicorn hair,

3103
01:53:51,360 --> 01:53:53,880
eight and a half inches, springy.

3104
01:53:53,880 --> 01:53:55,280
Go on, go on,

3105
01:53:55,280 --> 01:53:56,240
try it out."

3106
01:53:56,240 --> 01:53:58,320
Harry tried. And tried.

3107
01:53:58,320 --> 01:54:02,280
He had no idea what Mr. 
Ollivander was waiting for.

3108
01:54:02,280 --> 01:54:06,360
The pile of tried wands was mounting 
higher and higher on the spindly chair,

3109
01:54:06,360 --> 01:54:09,440
but the more wands Mr. Ollivander 
pulled from the shelves,

3110
01:54:09,440 --> 01:54:11,320
the happier he seemed to become.

3111
01:54:11,320 --> 01:54:13,160
"Tricky customer, eh?

3112
01:54:13,160 --> 01:54:14,000
Not to worry,

3113
01:54:14,000 --> 01:54:16,160
we'll find the perfect match here somewhere ,

3114
01:54:16,160 --> 01:54:18,280
I wonder, now - - yes,

3115
01:54:18,280 --> 01:54:20,640
why not , unusual combination ,

3116
01:54:20,640 --> 01:54:22,400
holly and phoenix feather,

3117
01:54:22,400 --> 01:54:23,240
eleven inches,

3118
01:54:23,240 --> 01:54:24,520
nice and supple."

3119
01:54:24,520 --> 01:54:25,840
Harry took the wand.

3120
01:54:25,840 --> 01:54:28,120
He felt a sudden warmth in his fingers.

3121
01:54:28,120 --> 01:54:29,880
He raised the wand above his head,

3122
01:54:29,880 --> 01:54:32,040
brought it swishing down through the dusty air

3123
01:54:32,040 --> 01:54:35,840
and a stream of red and gold sparks 
shot from the end like a firework,

3124
01:54:35,840 --> 01:54:38,600
throwing dancing spots of light on to the walls.

3125
01:54:38,600 --> 01:54:41,760
Hagrid whooped and clapped 
and Mr. Ollivander cried,

3126
01:54:41,760 --> 01:54:43,080
"Oh, bravo!

3127
01:54:43,080 --> 01:54:44,600
Yes, indeed,

3128
01:54:44,600 --> 01:54:46,200
oh, very good.

3129
01:54:46,200 --> 01:54:48,120
Well, well, well...

3130
01:54:48,120 --> 01:54:49,080
how curious...

3131
01:54:49,080 --> 01:54:50,240
how very curious...

3132
01:54:50,240 --> 01:54:50,920
"

3133
