3148
01:55:20,480 --> 01:55:21,880
Harry swallowed.

3149
01:55:21,880 --> 01:55:24,960
"Yes, thirteen-and-a-half inches. Yew.

3150
01:55:24,960 --> 01:55:27,680
Curious indeed how these things happen.

3151
01:55:27,680 --> 01:55:29,320
The wand chooses the wizard,

3152
01:55:29,320 --> 01:55:30,200
remember....

3153
01:55:30,200 --> 01:55:32,640
I think we must expect great things from you,

3154
01:55:32,640 --> 01:55:33,760
Mr. Potter....

3155
01:55:33,760 --> 01:55:37,440
After all, He- Who-Must-Not-Be-Named 
did great things ,

3156
01:55:37,440 --> 01:55:38,520
terrible, yes,

3157
01:55:38,520 --> 01:55:39,520
