3158
01:55:39,520 --> 01:55:40,640
Harry shivered.

3159
01:55:40,640 --> 01:55:43,640
He wasn't sure he liked Mr. Ollivander too much.

3160
01:55:43,640 --> 01:55:46,000
He paid seven gold Galleons for his wand,

3161
01:55:46,000 --> 01:55:48,560
and Mr. Ollivander bowed them from his shop.

3162
01:55:48,560 --> 01:55:51,160
The late afternoon sun hung 
low in the sky as Harry

3163
