sat down on plastic seats to eat them.

3175
01:56:25,640 --> 01:56:27,280
Harry kept looking around.

3176
01:56:27,280 --> 01:56:29,520
Everything looked so strange, somehow.

3177
01:56:29,520 --> 01:56:32,240
"You all right, Harry? Yer very quiet,"

3178
01:56:32,240 --> 01:56:33,240
said Hagrid.

3179
01:56:33,240 --> 01:56:35,200
Harry wasn't sure he could explain.

3180
01:56:35,200 --> 01:56:37,840
He'd just had the best birthday of his life ,

3181
01:56:37,840 --> 01:56:39,800
and yet , he chewed his hamburger,

3182
01:56:39,800 --> 01:56:41,600
