3882
02:20:49,720 --> 02:20:52,560
She sat down. Ron looked taken aback.

3883
02:20:52,560 --> 02:20:54,081
"Er , all right."

3884
02:20:54,080 --> 02:20:55,519
He cleared his throat.

3885
02:20:55,520 --> 02:21:00,480
"Sunshine, daisies, butter mellow, 
Turn this stupid, fat rat yellow."

3886
02:21:00,479 --> 02:21:01,799
He waved his wand,

3887
02:21:01,800 --> 02:21:03,120
