3888
02:21:03,120 --> 02:21:05,760
Scabbers stayed gray and fast asleep.

3889
02:21:05,760 --> 02:21:07,480
"Are you sure that's a real spell?"

3890
02:21:07,479 --> 02:21:08,679
said the girl.

3891
02:21:08,680 --> 02:21:11,120
"Well, it's not very good, is it?

