02:21:42,640 --> 02:21:43,680
"I'm Ron Weasley,"

3909
02:21:43,680 --> 02:21:44,760
Ron muttered.

3910
02:21:44,760 --> 02:21:45,680
"Harry Potter,"

3911
02:21:45,680 --> 02:21:46,680
said Harry.

3912
02:21:46,680 --> 02:21:47,720
"Are you really?"

3913
02:21:47,720 --> 02:21:48,880
said Hermione.

3914
02:21:48,880 --> 02:21:49,920
"I know all about you,

3915
02:21:49,920 --> 02:21:50,760
of course ,

