3920
02:21:57,479 --> 02:22:00,319
and Great Wizarding Events 
of the Twentieth Century.

3921
02:22:00,319 --> 02:22:01,040
"Am I?"

3922
02:22:01,040 --> 02:22:03,040
said Harry, feeling dazed.

3923
02:22:03,040 --> 02:22:04,600
"Goodness, didn't you know,

3924
