3935
02:22:27,160 --> 02:22:29,840
And she left, taking the toadless boy with her.

3936
02:22:29,840 --> 02:22:32,080
"Whatever house I'm in, I hope she's not in it,"

3937
02:22:32,080 --> 02:22:35,760
